\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon-16x16.png\" sizes=\"16x16\" type=\"image/png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"\n          geist_9e050971-module__05dp7a__className\n          bg-[#F7F6F3]\n          text-neutral-900\n          antialiased\n        \"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\"><header class=\"   sticky   top-0   z-50   border-b   border-neutral-200/60   bg-[#F7F6F3]/90   backdrop-blur-md   \"><div class=\"   mx-auto   flex   max-w-[1280px]   items-center   justify-between   px-6   py-5   \"><a class=\"   text-xl   font-light   tracking-[0.25em]   uppercase   text-neutral-900   \" href=\"/\">tinysorted</a><nav class=\"   hidden   md:flex   items-center   gap-8   text-sm   text-neutral-600   \"><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/minimalist-living\">Minimalist Living</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/storage-ideas\">Storage Ideas</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/kitchen\">kitchen</a><a class=\"   hover:text-neutral-900   transition   \" href=\"/category/small-spaces\">Small Spaces</a></nav><a aria-label=\"Search\" class=\"   flex   items-center   justify-center   w-10   h-10   rounded-full   border   border-neutral-200   hover:bg-white   transition   \" href=\"/search\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></a></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><!--$--><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#F7F6F3]\"><section class=\"   max-w-[1100px]   mx-auto   px-6   \"><header class=\"   pt-24   pb-20   \"><p class=\"   uppercase   tracking-[0.25em]   text-xs   text-neutral-500   mb-5   \">Editorial</p><h1 class=\"   text-5xl   md:text-7xl   font-light   tracking-[-0.04em]   leading-none   \">Editorial Policy</h1><p class=\"   mt-8   max-w-3xl   text-xl   leading-9   text-neutral-600   \">Everything we publish follows a clear editorial process designed to deliver practical, trustworthy, and easy-to-understand content.</p></header><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Our Editorial Mission</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted exists to help readers create homes that are cleaner, calmer, and more functional.</p><p>Every article is written with one goal: provide practical advice that readers can actually apply in everyday life.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">How We Create Content</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Before publishing an article we conduct research from reputable sources, industry publications, product documentation, and real-world experience whenever possible.</p><p>Our articles are written to explain concepts clearly, avoid unnecessary jargon, and focus on practical solutions.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Fact Checking</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Accuracy matters.</p><p>Whenever possible we verify facts using multiple trusted sources before publication.</p><p>If an error is identified, we review it and update the article as quickly as possible.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Product Recommendations</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>TinySorted occasionally recommends products that help readers organize and improve their living spaces.</p><p>Products are selected based on:</p><ul class=\"mt-6 list-disc space-y-3 pl-6\"><li>Practical usefulness</li><li>Build quality</li><li>Reader value</li><li>Overall reputation</li><li>Suitability for small-space living</li></ul></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Affiliate Relationships</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Some recommended products contain affiliate links.</p><p>These relationships never influence our editorial decisions.</p><p>Products are recommended because we believe they provide value—not because of commissions.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Article Updates</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Home organization trends, product availability, and best practices change over time.</p><p>We periodically review older articles to keep them accurate and relevant.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Corrections</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Despite careful review, mistakes can occasionally happen.</p><p>If you notice inaccurate information, please contact us. We appreciate constructive feedback and will investigate every report.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Editorial Independence</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Our editorial team works independently from advertisers and affiliate partners.</p><p>Brands cannot purchase favorable reviews or influence our recommendations.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"   text-3xl   font-light   mb-6   \">Contact the Editorial Team</h2><div class=\"   space-y-6      text-lg   leading-9   text-neutral-700   \"><p>Questions about our editorial standards can be sent to:</p><p class=\"mt-6 font-medium\">editor@tinysorted.com</p></div></section></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"   mt-40   border-t   border-neutral-200   bg-[#F7F6F3]   \"><div class=\"   mx-auto   max-w-[1280px]   px-6   py-24   \"><div class=\"   grid   gap-16      md:grid-cols-2   lg:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]   \"><div><a href=\"/\"><h2 class=\"   text-2xl   font-light   uppercase   tracking-[0.32em]   text-neutral-900   transition   hover:opacity-70   \">Tinysorted</h2></a><p class=\"   mt-6   max-w-xl   text-neutral-600   leading-8   \">TinySorted helps people organize small spaces, simplify everyday living, and discover practical home solutions through thoughtfully researched articles and carefully selected product recommendations.</p><p class=\"   mt-6   text-sm   text-neutral-500   \">Practical ideas for better living.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Explore</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/decluttering\">Decluttering</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/small-spaces\">Small Spaces</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/storage-ideas\">Storage Ideas</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/category/kitchen\">Kitchen</a></nav></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Company</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/write-for-us\">Write For Us</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/advertise\">Advertise</a></nav></div><div><h3 class=\"   mb-6   text-xs   uppercase   tracking-[0.24em]   text-neutral-500   \">Legal</h3><nav class=\"space-y-4\"><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/affiliate-disclosure\">Affiliate Disclosure</a><a class=\"block hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/disclaimer\">Disclaimer</a></nav></div></div><div class=\"   mt-20   border-t   border-neutral-200   pt-10   \"><p class=\"   max-w-4xl   text-sm   leading-7   text-neutral-500   \">TinySorted participates in various affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through links on this site, at no additional cost to you. Our recommendations are based on independent research and editorial judgment.</p></div><div class=\"   mt-12   flex   flex-col   gap-4      border-t   border-neutral-200   pt-8      md:flex-row   md:items-center   md:justify-between   \"><p class=\"   text-sm   text-neutral-500   \">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> TinySorted. All rights reserved.</p><div class=\"   flex   flex-wrap   gap-6      text-sm   text-neutral-500   \"><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/sitemap.xml\">Sitemap</a><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/rss.xml\">RSS</a><a class=\"hover:text-black transition\" href=\"/contact\">Support</a></div></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14rn1owgzaaej.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"LoadingBoundaryProvider\\\"]\\n2:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n3:I[79520,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/114nxh_ygt_qp.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/ch